 Hvala, Hvala, Hvala!

278
00:26:37,280 --> 00:26:39,280
 Hvala, Hvala, Hvala!

279
00:26:39,280 --> 00:26:41,280
 Hvala, Hvala, Hvala, Hvala!

280
00:26:41,280 --> 00:26:43,280
 Hvala, Hvala, Hvala, Hvala!

281
00:26:43,280 --> 00:26:45,280
 Hvala, Hvala, Hvala, Hvala!

282
00:26:45,280 --> 00:26:47,280
 Hvala, Hvala, Hvala, Hvala!

283
