2116
02:00:03,900 --> 02:00:09,900
 Yes, I will not be able to give the European Commission's views on this.

2117
02:00:09,900 --> 02:00:12,900
 Because this is clearly a highly complex issue.

2118
02:00:12,900 --> 02:00:15,900
 Which is also a very country-specific issue.

2119
02:00:15,900 --> 02:00:21,900
 There's no answer that you could give by looking just at the horizontal issues.

2120
02:00:21,900 --> 02:00:27,900
 Of course, first of all, you should never rush in any of these decisions.

2121
02:00:27,900 --> 02:00:31,900
 I mean, rushing into such a system is certainly not good advice.

2122
02:00:31,900 --> 02:00:40,900
 This should be done always on the basis of very deep and comprehensive consideration of all aspects.

2123
02:00:40,900 --> 02:00:42,900
 And involving all stakeholders.

2124
02:00:42,900 --> 02:00:45,900
 Certainly, if you move towards banking union.

2125
02:00:45,900 --> 02:00:48,900
 And you join in a cooperative agreement.

2126
02:00:48,900 --> 02:00:51,900
 You give up some competences.

2127
02:00:51,900 --> 02:00:52,900
 That's clear.

2128
02:00:52,900 --> 02:00:54,900
 And you risk disagreement.

2129
02:00:54,900 --> 02:00:57,900
 I think that is one of the key aspects.

2130
02:00:57,900 --> 02:01:00,900
 It's clear that if decisions are taken in Frankfurt.

2131
02:01:00,900 --> 02:01:04,900
 They may not be the one that you would have taken on your own.

2132
02:01:04,900 --> 02:01:05,900
 And that is clear.

2133
02:01:05,900 --> 02:01:08,900
 You need to be aware how to deal with such a situation.

2134
02:01:08,900 --> 02:01:10,900
 Of course, there's rules and procedures.

2135
02:01:10,900 --> 02:01:11,900
 Protocols.

2136
02:01:11,900 --> 02:01:13,900
 But in the end, it's also a political issue.

2137
02:01:13,900 --> 02:01:16,900
 Are you capable of acting in such an environment?

2138
02:01:16,900 --> 02:01:18,900
 You do gain something.

2139
02:01:18,900 --> 02:01:21,900
 Maybe you don't gain everything.

2140
02:01:21,900 --> 02:01:25,900
 You don't get the entire third floor of your high rise already.

2141
02:01:25,900 --> 02:01:30,900
 But you do gain wider expertise that is being accumulated in Frankfurt.

2142
02:01:30,900 --> 02:01:34,900
 And you gain the horizontal view of issues.

2143
02:01:34,900 --> 02:01:40,900
 And I think that is something that maybe sometimes not fully emphasized in the discussion.

2144
02:01:40,900 --> 02:01:45,900
 I was saying earlier in a private conversation.

2145
02:01:45,900 --> 02:01:48,900
 No matter where you go, you will never find anybody.

2146
02:01:48,900 --> 02:01:50,900
 Who is saying yes, you are right.

2147
02:01:50,900 --> 02:01:53,900
 Our national supervisory system is not really good.

2148
02:01:53,900 --> 02:01:55,900
 And we should jump to another one.

2149
02:01:55,900 --> 02:01:57,900
 You know, nobody would ever say that.

2150
02:01:57,900 --> 02:02:09,900
 And even the most countries which experiences a massive banking crisis would say to you on the week before the major bank collapses.

2151
02:02:09,900 --> 02:02:10,900
 Everything is fine.

2152
02:02:10,900 --> 02:02:13,900
 You know, I've never heard anybody saying that.

2153
02:02:13,900 --> 02:02:14,900
 Yeah, you're right.

2154
02:02:14,900 --> 02:02:16,900
 My supervisor system is not really working.

2155
02:02:16,900 --> 02:02:19,900
 This is just this is an argument that will never come.

2156
02:02:19,900 --> 02:02:24,900
 So you shouldn't wait until anybody in your country or your discussions is saying.

2157
02:02:24,900 --> 02:02:26,900
 Look, you know, this is not performing.

2158
02:02:26,900 --> 02:02:27,900
 You should change it.

2159
02:02:27,900 --> 02:02:31,900
 This is not realistic to wait for.

2160
02:02:31,900 --> 02:02:35,900
 So coming back to the more more concrete case.

2161
02:02:35,900 --> 02:02:40,900
 Yes, there's costs and benefits.

2162
02:02:40,900 --> 02:02:52,900
 And I fully agree that at the current state the case for for waiting is certainly should be should be taken and considered seriously.

2163
02:02:52,900 --> 02:02:59,900
 But from from all the presentations this morning, you probably saw you get the feeling this is a moving process.

2164
02:02:59,900 --> 02:03:01,900
 This is a train moving.

2165
02:03:01,900 --> 02:03:02,900
 It's not always very fast.

2166
02:03:02,900 --> 02:03:07,900
 It's currently maybe it may be a bit slow moving train, but it is moving.

2167
02:03:07,900 --> 02:03:14,900
 And there may be also in a time when it's too late when things get even more difficult to jump on the train.

2168
02:03:14,900 --> 02:03:24,900
 And that is I think should always be part of the consideration the wait and see strategy is always sounds nice in the operation of the day to day framework.

2169
02:03:24,900 --> 02:03:42,900
 But if you look at the wider orientation, which is certainly favorable towards the euro area, then there may be an issue saying, you know, why should we, you know, at least be aware that waiting can also be too long.

2170
02:03:42,900 --> 02:03:44,900
 Thank you.

2171
02:03:44,900 --> 02:03:46,900
 Thank you.

2172
02:03:46,900 --> 02:03:53,140
 Imaju li banke uopće jedinstveni stav o ovom pitanju i ako imaju, kakav je?

2173
02:03:53,140 --> 02:04:01,700
 Da, ovo je dobro pitanje i dobro je da ste danas to isto stavili pred ovaj skup.

2174
02:04:01,700 --> 02:04:08,720
 Da, videli smo iz izlaganja vice guvernera Šošića da je pitanje prilaska,

2175
02:04:08,720 --> 02:04:16,400
 neću reći namjerno ulaska u Bankovnu uniju relativno čvrsto ili duboko vezano

2176
02:04:16,400 --> 02:04:21,440
 i u krajnji liniji sa pitanjem pristupa i prilaza Hrvatske eurozoni.

2177
02:04:21,440 --> 02:04:31,080
 Dakle, dva su moguća pristupa da, kao što smo čuli prije nekoliko mjeseci izjavu i predsjednica,

2178
02:04:31,080 --> 02:04:37,800
 a zatim i našeg predsjednika vlade, idemo brzo u eurozonu, dakle uvešemo euro.

2179
02:04:38,520 --> 02:04:42,200
 Naravno, što bi značilo brzo, to za sad nitko nije definirao.

2180
02:04:42,200 --> 02:04:46,660
 Ako bi to bilo u nekakvom roku od pet godina, onda se postavlja pitanje

2181
02:04:46,660 --> 02:04:50,080
 trebali Hrvatsku dalje deurizirati.

2182
02:04:50,080 --> 02:04:55,340
 Naime, vidjeli ste, većina vas je upoznata da je potražnja građana,

2183
02:04:55,340 --> 02:05:01,480
 a i potražnja korporativnog sektora za čistim kunskim kreditima sve veća.

2184
02:05:01,480 --> 02:05:07,340
 Ako Hrvatska izabere, a morala bi izabrati jedan od tih puteva nekakve spore,

2185
02:05:08,320 --> 02:05:14,160
 korog pristupa ili prilaza eurozoni, a to znači nekakvih deset ili petnaest godina,

2186
02:05:14,160 --> 02:05:19,760
 onda ćemo se svi sasvim sigurno dugačije ponašati u svemu tomu.

2187
02:05:19,760 --> 02:05:25,900
 Prema Hrvatska je pred nekakvom odlukom eurizirati se ili ne eurizirati,

2188
02:05:25,900 --> 02:05:28,460
 i to mora na neki način biti raspravljeno.

2189
02:05:28,540 --> 02:05:34,380
 Mi smo kao Hrvatska odruga Banaka tu temu već tijeli staviti na jedan veći skup,

2190
02:05:34,380 --> 02:05:40,220
 širi skup, možda konferenciju, gdje bi pozvali mnoge stakeholders da se udjeluju u svem o tome.

2191
02:05:40,220 --> 02:05:46,760
 Ali da, Hrvatska stoji pred odlukom hoće li se eurozirati ili deurizirati i mi moramo tu odluku donijeti.

2192
02:05:46,760 --> 02:05:53,560
 O tome ovisi mnogo budućih poteza, dakle i kad ćemo ući u bankovnu uniju, a i neke druge staje.

2193
02:05:55,560 --> 02:06:02,900
 Dakle, zapravo, odgovor o ulazku u bankarsku uniju je direktno vezan uz ulazak u eurozonu,

2194
02:06:02,900 --> 02:06:04,920
 odnosno prihvaćanje eura, po vašem mišljenju.

2195
02:06:04,920 --> 02:06:13,620
 Evo, last but not least, domaćinima zadnje pitanje, osvrtna na ovu zapravo ključnu temu,

2196
02:06:13,620 --> 02:06:21,060
 iako je gospodin Šošić već to elaborirao, siguran sam da ćete vi, gospodine Odak, imati još nešto za dodati.

2197
02:06:22,560 --> 02:06:28,040
 Da, naravno, to je zanimljiva tema za pričati, možemo o njoj puno pričati,

2198
02:06:28,040 --> 02:06:33,740
 međutim, prvo ovo, kako je gospodin Rotter vrlo jasno rekao, to je političko pitanje.

2199
02:06:33,740 --> 02:06:40,960
 Znači, odluku o tome da li ćemo ići u close cooperation ili ne, donosi zakonodavac.

2200
02:06:40,960 --> 02:06:47,320
 Competent authority, znači Hrvatska narodna banka, može o tome imati svoje mišljenje.

2201
02:06:47,320 --> 02:06:52,320
 To mišljenje na zahtjev zakonodavca može i prezentirati, tako da ono bude formalno,

2202
02:06:53,220 --> 02:06:56,200
 što se do sada, koliko ja znam, nije dogodilo.

2203
02:06:56,200 --> 02:07:08,200
 Znači, mi ovo što govorimo, to su naši stavovi koje imamo, koji su individualni, koji su uskladženi na razine institucije,

2204
02:07:08,200 --> 02:07:09,920
 ali koji nisu službeni.

2205
02:07:09,920 --> 02:07:13,660
 Niti su do sada oslužbenjeni, niti smo mi tu oni koji donosimo odlu.

2206
02:07:14,040 --> 02:07:20,460
 Ako bude postojao zahtjev za pružanje savjeta, mi ćemo bilo saboru ili vladi taj savjet pružiti.

2207
02:07:23,120 --> 02:07:29,220
 Pitanje je ovo koje je Zdenko otvorio, eurizirati se ili deurizirati.

2208
02:07:31,360 --> 02:07:34,580
 Ja ne vidim političnost te odluke.

2209
02:07:34,580 --> 02:07:39,320
 To je odluka koju donosi 4 miliona stanovnika ove zemlje svaki za sebe,

2210
02:07:39,320 --> 02:07:43,580
 stavljajući u novčanik euro ili kunu.

2211
02:07:43,580 --> 02:07:49,320
 I ne znam koja konferencija će utjecati na 4 miliona stanovnika da prebace jedno u drugo,

2212
02:07:50,200 --> 02:07:56,000
 ali sam potpuno siguran da dogod se govori moramo ići u kunu da bi se kuna devalvirala,

2213
02:07:56,000 --> 02:07:58,200
 da niko razuma neće ići u kunu.

2214
02:07:58,200 --> 02:08:04,500
 Nego će čekati da se desi ta devalvacija, pa će onda otići u kunu da pobere ono što može pobjeti.

2215
02:08:04,500 --> 02:08:09,220
 Znači, odluka je upravo na razini komunikacije, na razini struke.

2216
02:08:09,220 --> 02:08:16,000
 Ako narodu vrlo jasno kažemo da je kuna čvrsta i stabilna valuta

2217
02:08:16,000 --> 02:08:20,600
 i za koje stoje sve političke opcije ove zemlje, da ljudi će je ozbiljno shvatiti.

2218
02:08:20,600 --> 02:08:26,840
 Ako kažemo ne, kuna nije, kuna nam je tu alat da se ostvare interesi određenih skupina,

2219
02:08:26,840 --> 02:08:32,920
 kuna će biti alat, ali ne očekujte da će ljudi izvan svoje dnevne transakcije držati kune,

2220
02:08:32,920 --> 02:08:34,620
 jer su pametni.

2221
02:08:34,620 --> 02:08:40,660
 Znači, konferencija je zgodna i praktična stvar, možemo se uvijek naći,

2222
02:08:40,660 --> 02:08:44,000
 to je dobro, lijepo popričati poslije popitkavicu,

2223
02:08:45,340 --> 02:08:50,420
 ali mi moramo utjecati na 4 miliona pametnih ljudi da donesu pametnu odluku da drže kunu

2224
02:08:50,420 --> 02:08:55,240
 i onda ćemo se deurizirati, ako to želim.

2225
02:08:55,240 --> 02:09:00,880
 A možda ipak praktičniji put, pođer smo već potpisali ugovor Otić u Euro

2226
02:09:00,880 --> 02:09:05,300
 i onda naravno sami time i u single supervisor i mehanizam,

2227
02:09:05,460 --> 02:09:11,340
 ali tu isto tako mi očekujemo i od komisije i od Evropske središnje banke

2228
02:09:11,340 --> 02:09:16,540
 da umjesto formalne ponude koje je sad na stolu donese stvarnu ponudu.

2229
02:09:17,280 --> 02:09:22,360
 i kaže ljudi, mi vas hoćemo u SSM-u. Kad nam to komisija i ECB kažu,

2230
02:09:22,360 --> 02:09:25,940
 mi ćemo u SSM-u. A recite nam da nas tamo hoćete.

2231
02:09:25,940 --> 02:09:31,940
 Ne samo riječima, nego i ponudu. Eto, ja bih toliko rekao.

2232
02:09:34,340 --> 02:09:40,920
 Hvala lijepa. Nemam niti ambiciju, niti mandat, bilo što zaokruživati i zaključivati.

2233
02:09:40,920 --> 02:09:45,960
 Mogu jedino reći da ako vrijedi ona da svi putovi vode u Rim,

2234
02:09:45,960 --> 02:09:51,580
 a onda je ova rasprava pokazala da sve rasprave vode u priču o tečaju.

2235
02:09:51,580 --> 02:09:58,800
 O čemu god mi pričali u Hrvatskoj, ne možemo pobjeći od pitanja tečaja i eurizacije,

2236
02:09:58,800 --> 02:10:04,020
 ali to je ipak tema za neki drugi skup, iako je viceguvrner rekao

2237
02:10:04,020 --> 02:10:08,880
 da možda taj skup i osim kavice i tako dalje nema baš previše smisla,

2238
02:10:08,880 --> 02:10:15,820
 jer odluke donose neki drugi klijenti, oni koji štede, oni koji traže kredite.

2239
02:10:15,820 --> 02:10:22,080
 Ništa, ako nema daljnjih pitanja i komentara, ja bih se prije svega želio

2240
02:10:22,440 --> 02:10:28,840
 zahvaliti domaćinima i nakon toga i našim današnjim sudjelnicima okruglog stola,

2241
02:10:28,840 --> 02:10:35,920
 gospodinu Rotteru, gospodinu Adroviću, gospodinu Odaku i predlažim da ih pozdravimo sa Ljeskom.

2242
02:10:45,660 --> 02:10:51,680
 U ime HNB-a i Evropske komisije, hvala vam svima na dolazku i sudjelovanju

2243
02:10:51,680 --> 02:10:56,900
 i predlažim da se družimo malo ispred Gorane na Domjenku.

